<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ك س د:</span> <span class="c2">(كَسَدَ)</span> الشَّيْءُ يَكْسُدُ بِالضَّمِّ كَسَادًا فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(كَاسِدٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(كَسِيدٌ)</span> . وَسِلْعَةٌ <span class="c2">(كَاسِدَةٌ)</span> . وَسُوقٌ <span class="c2">(كَاسِدٌ)</span> بِلَا هَاءٍ. وَ <span class="c2">(أَكْسَدَ)</span> الرَّجُلُ كَسَدَتْ سُوقُهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>